Overview
Build the complete PromptHub backend: 82 endpoints across 14 domains, from an empty project skeleton to a fully functional API. The codebase follows a domain-driven folder structure under app/domains/.

IMPORTANT

This plan covers the full backend implementation. It is broken into 5 sequential phases. Each phase builds on the prior one. I will implement all phases after approval.

