Database Schema — All Tables
Below is the complete data model. All tables use SQLModel with UUID primary keys and UTC timestamps.

Creator (User) Table
python
class Creator(SQLModel, table=True):
    id: uuid.UUID (PK, default=uuid4)
    email: str (unique, indexed)
    hashed_password: str
    full_name: str | None
    handle: str | None (unique, indexed)  # @handle
    subdomain: str | None (unique, indexed)  # creator.prompthub.com
    bio: str | None
    avatar_url: str | None
    role: str (default="user")  # "user" | "admin"
    is_verified: bool (default=False)
    is_onboarded: bool (default=False)
    is_active: bool (default=True)  # soft-delete flag
    created_at: datetime (default=utcnow)
    updated_at: datetime (default=utcnow, on_update=utcnow)
RefreshToken Table
python
class RefreshToken(SQLModel, table=True):
    id: uuid.UUID (PK)
    creator_id: uuid.UUID (FK -> creator.id, indexed)
    token_hash: str (unique)
    expires_at: datetime
    is_revoked: bool (default=False)
    created_at: datetime
