AggregatedStat Table (cron-rolled)
python
class AggregatedStat(SQLModel, table=True):
    id: uuid.UUID (PK)
    creator_id: uuid.UUID (FK -> creator.id, indexed)
    stat_date: date (indexed)
    entity_type: str  # "prompt" | "portfolio" | "campaign"
    entity_id: uuid.UUID | None (indexed)
    views: int (default=0)
    copies: int (default=0)
    ad_impressions: int (default=0)
    ad_clicks: int (default=0)
    email_captures: int (default=0)
    # Unique constraint: (creator_id, stat_date, entity_type, entity_id)
